# Synapse Smart Contract Environment

## Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values:

```bash
# Private key for deployment (without 0x prefix)
PRIVATE_KEY=your_private_key_here

# 0G Testnet RPC URL
OG_RPC_URL=https://evmrpc-testnet.0g.ai

# 0G Storage Indexer URL (for metadata storage)
OG_INDEXER_URL=https://indexer-storage-testnet.0g.ai
```

## Contract Addresses (ADI Testnet - Chain ID 16602)

After deployment, contract addresses will be logged and saved to `deployments/0g-testnet.json`.

## Available Commands

```bash
# Compile contracts
npx hardhat compile

# Run tests
npx hardhat test

# Deploy to 0G Testnet
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.ts --network 0g-testnet

# Verify contracts (if supported)
npx hardhat verify --network 0g-testnet <CONTRACT_ADDRESS> <CONSTRUCTOR_ARGS>
```

